# !MODULE: HEMCO_Config.rc
#
# !DESCRIPTION: Contains configuration information for HEMCO.  Define the
#  emissions inventories and corresponding file paths here.
#\\
#\\
# !REMARKS:
#  The following tokens will be replaced:
#  (1) ROOT : Filepath to HEMCO root directory
#  (2) MET  : Met field type (from G-C compilation command)
#  (3) GRID : Horizontal grid type (from G-C compilation command)
#  (4) SIM  : Simulation type (from G-C compilation command)
#  (5) NEST : Nested-grid type (CH, EU, NA, SE)
#  (6) LNOX : String for OTD/LIS lightning NOx files:
#             (a) For GEOS-5 this is either "geos5.1.0" or "geos5.2.0".  
#             (b) For other met fields, this is the same as MET.
#  (7) LEVRED  : String w/ the # of levels in the reduced GEOS-Chem grid
#                as used in some filenames (e.g. "23L", "30L", "47L")
#  (8) LEVFULL : String w/ the # of levels in the full GEOS-Chem grid
#                as used in some filenames (e.g. "55L", "72L")
# 
# !REMARKS:
#  Customized for the CO2 specialty simulation.
#
# !REVISION HISTORY: 
#  17 Apr 2014 - C. Keller   - Initial version
#  07 Oct 2014 - R. Yantosca - Now use HEMCO tokens $ROOT, $MET, $RES
!  20 Oct 2014 - R. Yantosca - Now read GFED3 data from GFED3/v2014-10
#EOP
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#BOC
#

